/******************************************************************/
/* Program kicker is used to control the BNC-632 Waveform         */
/*    Generator to control the beam to LeRIBSS                    */
/*                                                                */
/* To be compiled with: gcc -lm -o kicker kicker.c                */
/*                                                                */
/* C. J. Gross, February 2009                                     */
/******************************************************************/

